show.description: He thought she'd be nothing without him—until she returned richer, stronger, and absolutely untouchable. This audio show unpacks a whirlwind journey of heartbreak, revenge, and billion-dollar power moves. Tune in to witness how a woman turns betrayal into unstoppable success.
